In 2020, shortly after the election, the CEO of <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#faux">Faux News</a> ordered that
<a href="https://boingboing.net/2023/03/30/fox-news-ceo-said-fact-checking-has-to-stop-now-because-it-is-bad-for-business.html">fact-checking "has to stop now"</a> because it is "bad for business".

 